description:
Wow. That's all we can say about this impressive 24 year old stud's ripped body. Mike is in amazing shape, and we think that if we measured his body fat, we'd find he doesn't have any. Only muscle on this guy. And this next door army dude is not shy when it comes to whipping out his most precious weapon. Watch out for this one. We're thrilled to have Mike as one of our Next Door Males. You'll be happy to have him too.

Watch Mike in three scenes... in the living room, relaxing in the kitchen, and then getting worked up in the bedroom before finally passing out week.
title: Mike
